  "text": "Remark 1.5. Compared with the result obtained by Chemin and Masmoudi in [CITATION_1] , we also obtain the global small solutions, yet there is no damping mechanism. Remark 1.6. Our methods can be used to other related models. Similar results for the compressible Oldroyd-B model will be given in a forthcoming paper.",
